  <brief_title>Study of LV5FU2 Versus FOLFOX for Curatively-resected, Node-positive Esophageal Squamous Cell Carcinoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Phase II Study of Leucovorin, 5-fluorouracil With or Without Oxaliplatin (LV5FU2 vs. FOLFOX) for Curatively-resected, Node-positive Esophageal Squamous Cell Carcinoma.</official_title>
